3.1.30 IsHalogen 
 
   
virtual bool IsHalogen() const
    
Determine whether an atom is a halogen atom.  This method tests
whether the atom is Fluorine, Chlorine, Bromine, Iodine or Astatine
(atomic number 9, 17, 35, 53 or 85).

  

  
          
     
        
